One-Person AI Army Business Toolkit (一人AI军团业务工具包)
This toolkit expands on the previous framework, converting the provided business list into practical sales materials. It includes a bilingual Quote Sheet, Statement of Work (SOW) Template, 3-tier Package Plans (Entry/Professional/Flagship), the Human-in-the-Loop SOP (refined from prior), and a standardized Delivery Package File Structure. These are designed for direct use in selling services, with placeholders for customization (e.g., your company name, pricing, specific business lines like content production or compliance support).
I've structured the packages around the 12 SKUs you listed, grouping them into tiers for scalability. Pricing is placeholder-based (e.g., [ENTRY_PRICE])—replace with your actual figures (e.g., $99/month for Entry). Assume a subscription model with optional one-time setups.

