2. Statement of Work (SOW) Template (工作说明书模板)
English Version
Project Title: [PROJECT_TITLE] (e.g., Monthly SEO Content Update)Scope: Delivery of [SKU_DESCRIPTION] as per Quote Sheet. Human commander oversees AI agents for tasks like [TASK_EXAMPLES].Deliverables:  

Final files in [FORMAT] (e.g., PDF/Markdown).  
Source list with citations.  
Change log and reproducibility notes.

Timeline: [START_DATE] to [END_DATE], with [MILESTONES].SLA: Response within [RESPONSE_TIME] hours; up to [REVISION_ROUNDS] revisions; fact-correction window of [WINDOW_DAYS] days.Compliance Points: AI usage disclosed; human final sign-off; data desensitized; non-legal advice only.Payment: [PAYMENT_SCHEDULE] (e.g., 50% upfront, 50% on delivery).Signatures: Client: ____________________ | Provider: ____________________ (Human Commander)  
Chinese Version (中文版本)
项目标题： [项目标题]（例如，每月SEO内容更新）范围： 根据报价单交付[SKU描述]。人类指挥官监督AI代理完成如[TASK_EXAMPLES]的任务。交付物：  

最终文件以[格式]（例如，PDF/Markdown）。  
带引用的来源清单。  
变更记录与可复现说明。

时间线： [开始日期]至[结束日期]，含[里程碑]。SLA： [响应时间]小时内响应；最多[修订轮次]次修订；事实纠错窗口为[窗口天数]天。合规要点： AI使用披露；人工最终签字；数据脱敏；仅非法律建议。支付： [支付计划]（例如，50%预付，50%交付后）。签名： 客户：____________________ | 提供方：____________________ (人类指挥官)  

3. 3-Tier Package Plans (3档套餐计划)
Entry Tier (入门级) - For startups/small businesses. Focus on low-regulation services (A category). Monthly subscription: [ENTRY_PRICE] (e.g., $499).  

Includes: SKUs 1-3 (Reports, Content, Social Assets).  
Features: Basic human review, standard SLA (2 revisions), email delivery.  
Ideal for: Quick content needs.

Professional Tier (专业级) - For mid-sized teams. Includes medium-regulation services (B-C). Monthly: [PRO_PRICE] (e.g., $999).  

Includes: SKUs 1-7 (Adds data, docs, monitoring).  
Features: Enhanced SLA (3 revisions, priority support), dashboard access, custom alerts.  
Ideal for: Ongoing operations and compliance.

Flagship Tier (旗舰级) - For enterprises. Covers all categories (A-F). Monthly: [FLAGSHIP_PRICE] (e.g., $1999) + project fees.  

Includes: All 12 SKUs, with customization.  
Features: Premium SLA (unlimited revisions in window, dedicated audits), insurance-backed, API integrations.  
Ideal for: High-stakes, regulated projects.

Chinese Version (中文版本)
入门级 - 适用于初创/小企业。聚焦低监管服务（A类）。月订阅：[ENTRY_PRICE]（例如，499美元）。  

包含：SKU 1-3（报告、内容、社媒素材）。  
特性：基本人工复核、标准SLA（2次修订）、邮件交付。  
适用于：快速内容需求。

专业级 - 适用于中型团队。包含中等监管服务（B-C）。月订阅：[PRO_PRICE]（例如，999美元）。  

包含：SKU 1-7（添加数据、文档、监控）。  
特性：增强SLA（3次修订、优先支持）、仪表盘访问、自定义告警。  
适用于：持续运营与合规。

旗舰级 - 适用于企业。覆盖所有类别（A-F）。月订阅：[FLAGSHIP_PRICE]（例如，1999美元）+项目费。  

包含：所有12 SKU，带定制。  
特性：高级SLA（窗口内无限修订、专用审计）、保险支持、API集成。  
适用于：高风险、监管项目。


4. Human-in-the-Loop SOP (人在环中SOP)
English Version (Refined for business delivery)  

Task Definition: Client request → Objectives → Criteria (sources, format, deadline).  
Data Handling: Minimal data, desensitized, sourced.  
Quality Control: AI draft → Auto-checks (facts/style) → Human review/sign-off.  
Delivery: Final version, archived logs, client notification.

Chinese Version (中文版本)  

任务定义： 客户请求 → 目标 → 标准（来源、格式、截止时间）。  
数据处理： 最小数据、脱敏、标注来源。  
质量控制： AI草案 → 自动检查（事实/风格） → 人工复核/签字。  
交付： 最终版本、归档日志、客户通知。


5. Delivery Package File Structure (交付包文件结构)
Delivery_Package_[PROJECT_ID]/
├── Final_Deliverables/  # 成品文件
│   ├── [MAIN_FILE].pdf/docx  # e.g., Report.pdf
│   └── [ASSETS]/  # e.g., Images/Scripts
├── Sources_and_Licenses/  # 来源/许可证清单
│   ├── Citations.csv  # Source links/timestamps
│   └── Licenses.txt  # Commercial use proofs
├── Change_Log.md  # 变更记录
├── Reproducibility_Notes.md  # 可复现说明 (prompts/models/scripts)
└── Audit_Log.json  # Optional: Human sign-off logs

This structure ensures traceability and compliance. Zip and deliver via secure link/email.

Customization Notes (定制说明)

Business Line Adaptation: Replace examples with your focus (e.g., if specializing in e-commerce, emphasize SKUs 8/3).  
Pricing Placeholders: Set based on costs (e.g., AI inference ~$0.01/task) + margin.  
Contract Integration: Link to prior MSA templates for AI disclosure, etc.  
Ready to sell: Use this in proposals—websites can embed the Quote Sheet as a form.
